https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jCyJN1vj8jqJJ0vNw4hDH2KlySO.jpg The iconic creatures from two of the scariest film franchises in movie history wage their most brutal battle ever—in our own backyard. The small town of Gunnison, Colorado becomes a war zone between two of the deadliest extra-terrestrial life forms—the Alien and the Predator. When a Predator scout ship crash-lands in the hills outside the town, Alien Facehuggers and a hybrid Alien/Predator are released and begin to terrorize the town. Aliens vs Predator: Requiem
